19:T41f,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a product family of glutaraldehyde-based high-level disinfectant solutions offered in 2% and 2.45% concentrations with activator. The brochure description provides specific clinical use cases (endoscopes, surgical equipment, heat-sensitive instruments) and positioning (hospital-grade, rapid sterilization). MyScan appears to be the product brand/line name under Meril Life Sciences' Infection Prevention division. External evidence confirms Meril Life Sciences manufactures infection prevention solutions but does not provide specific MyScan product details. Classification as product_family is appropriate as it represents a line of disinfectant solutions with multiple concentration options. No conflicts detected between internal evidence and external manufacturer verification. The current classification correctly identifies the active ingredient, concentrations, and manufacturer. Confidence is high based on complete internal documentation despite lack of detailed external MyScan-specific information.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution","product_name_display":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution","sku_code":"MS-GTA","product_family":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution","product_family_display":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution","slug":"myscan-glutaraldehyde-solution","images":[{"id":"f6c3e8b50c7b","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfade/cover_2f78c6f5.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Surgical Gowns Brochure 27-09-2025.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":262286,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:30.484849+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution | MyScan Instrument Disinfectants - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"MyScan Glutaraldehyde Solution is a hospital-grade instrument disinfectant featuring 2% and 2.45% glutarald